<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: #7c2d12; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
    .content { background: white; padding: 30px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; }
    .warning-box { background: #fef2f2; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid #dc2626; }
    .button { background: #dc2626; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; display: inline-block; }
    .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Account Suspended</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hi <%= @user.name || @user.email_address %>,</p>
      
      <div class="warning-box">
        <h3>⚠️ Your RepuTable account has been suspended</h3>
        <p>Due to overdue payment, we have temporarily suspended your account access. All your data is safe and will be restored immediately upon payment.</p>
      </div>
      
      <p><strong>What happened?</strong></p>
      <p>Your invoice payment is more than 7 days overdue, and we haven't received payment or payment confirmation from you.</p>
      
      <p><strong>What's affected?</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>You cannot access your dashboard, reviews, or campaigns</li>
        <li>Review collection campaigns are temporarily paused</li>
        <li>Email notifications are suspended</li>
      </ul>
      
      <p><strong>How to restore access:</strong></p>
      <ol>
        <li>Make payment for all outstanding invoices</li>
        <li>Upload payment proof in your account</li>
        <li>We'll verify and restore access within 24 hours</li>
      </ol>
      
      <p style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
        <a href="<%= Rails.application.routes.url_helpers.billing_overview_url(host: 'reputable.co') %>" class="button">
          Restore Account
        </a>
      </p>
      
      <p>We understand that payment issues can happen. If you need assistance or have questions, please contact us immediately.</p>
      
      <p>Thanks,<br>
      The RepuTable Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>RepuTable - Reputation Management Made Simple</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>